TEXT.P:
Outstanding in this good cast are Arnie Burton as the twins, one
foolish, lustful and rich and the other ridiculously honorable;
Robin Leslie Brown as an impudent maid with an eye for aroused men;
Clement Fowler as a bumbling hypocrite, a kind of rural Tartuffe,
and Kevin Black as a competitor in romance to the honorable twin,
one of the more endearing idiots in stage literature.
